articles.title: About this site
articles.description: Details about myself and this project
articles.contents:
About Me
Hi, my name is Tejas Mundhe and I am an incoming freshman at Walnut Hills High School. I enjoy playing soccer and swimming as well as having a passion for computer science.
About the Project
This project was made through Kaneâ€™s Free High School Data Science Bootcamp to explore the popular theory that more elite athletes are born in January. To investigate this I sorted the number of Euro 2021 players birthdays for each month and made that data into a bar graph
Conclusion
After making and publishing this plot I learned that a comparable number of players were born in each month with January not being a outlier, proving the theory that more elite athletes are born in January false.

articles.title: Euro 2020 Player Birth Months
articles.description: A plot of the number of soccer players playing in Euro 2021 that are born in each month to investigate if more elite athletes are born in January.
